VALUES ('9759b553-6313-4111-8988-ac35cbb4b078', 'Which choice completes the text so that it conforms to the conventions of Standard English?', 'The monograph''s central term—predictive coding, a coinage its author, a notoriously precise stylist, defended at length—anchors the argument ______ that the later commentators, working from an abridged edition, persistently misread.', 'passage', '[{"id":"A","text":": a claim","is_correct":true,"explanation":"Correct: the boundary correctly attaches the non-restrictive appositive without splicing the clause."},{"id":"B","text":", a claim","is_correct":false,"explanation":"[Run-on] A surface-plausible mark that either splices independent clauses or mislocates the appositive boundary."},{"id":"C","text":"; a claim","is_correct":false,"explanation":"[Restrictive/Non-Restrictive] A surface-plausible mark that either splices independent clauses or mislocates the appositive boundary."},{"id":"D","text":" a claim","is_correct":false,"explanation":"[Comma Splice] A surface-plausible mark that either splices independent clauses or mislocates the appositive boundary."}]'::jsonb, 'A', 'Logical Reconstruction:
