correlation of this kind can ever, in any field, license a causal inference —under the scope the passage actually licenses.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"[Over-Extrapolation] Grounded in passage language but fails on a specific qualifier in its second sentence."}]'::jsonb, 'B', 'Logical Reconstruction:
